                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72111Sp1/88</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="frus1917Supp02v01#p_WJE1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Willard</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>[<date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research"
                        calendar="gregorian" when="1917-10-07">undated</date>]</dateline>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>815. Naval attaché just received following telegram from consular agent at Cadiz:
                    “German submarine interned Cadiz escaped.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1917Supp02v01#p_WJE1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Willard</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
